devdoc.details: Concrete implementation of GasVehicle representing a car.

constructor.details: Constructor to initialize the car's fuel tank size and fuel efficiency.

params._fuelTankSize: The size of the fuel tank.
params._kilometersPerLitre: The fuel efficiency of the car.

drive(uint256).details: Drives the vehicle for the specified distance.

fuelUp(uint256).details: Fuels up the vehicle with the specified amount of litres.

params.litres: The amount of fuel to add to the tank.

getFuelCapacity().details: Returns the fuel capacity of the car.

getKilometersPerLitre().details: Returns the kilometers per litre of the car.

kilometersRemaining().details: Returns the kilometers the vehicle can drive with the remaining fuel.

startEngine().details: Starts the engine of the vehicle.

stopEngine().details: Stops the engine of the vehicle.
